title: 84 Countries
description:
The Wilbur is only four days away and things are coming together as smoothly as you’d think. Dave is going back and forth about going to the Barstool Minigolf tournament tomorrow and not even he can explain his thought process. WFAN and Audacy are taking LIV golf money. Blind Mike and Justin play a geography game after Bill O’Reilly claims he has been to 84 countries. Bruce Springsteen tour dates announced, former Thursday guest is hired by Barstool Sports, calls and more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
